<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
      <%- include ('./partials/head.ejs') %>
  </head>
  <body class="text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <nav>
        <%- include ('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
      </nav>
<br>
<h3>Feel the need for some socially distant cycling competition?</h3>
<p>There will be a leaderboard for top sprints/hillclimbs around Austin</</br>Currently the only leaderboard is for the 1000ft drag on East 5th st.</br>
It starts east of Springdale Rd and lasts until you pass Spencer Ln.</p>
</div>
<div>

  <h1>1000 ft. drag</h1>

      <table class="table" id="table" data-toggle="table" data-sort-order="desc" data-sort-name="time">

  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Rider Name</th>
      <th data-field="time" data-sortable="true">Time</th>
      <th data-field="speed" data-sortable="true">Top Speed</th>
      <th></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
    <% for (let ride of rides) { %>
    <tr>
      <td><%= ride.username%> </td>
      <td class="time"><%= ride.time %></td>
      <td><%= ride.topSpeed %></td>
      <td><a href="/rides/<%=ride._id%>"><button type="button" name="Show">Ride Data</button></a></td>
    </tr>
<%}%>
  </table>

  <%if (currentUser) {%>
  <a href="/rides/new">
  <button type="button" name="New Ride" >
    Create New Ride
  </button>
  </a>
  <%}else{%>
  <h3>Log in to add a ride</h3>
  <%}%>
</div>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js" integrity="sha512-bLT0Qm9VnAYZDflyKcBaQ2gg0hSYNQrJ8RilYldYQ1FxQYoCLtUjuuRuZo+fjqhx/qtq/1itJ0C2ejDxltZVFg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/bootstrap-table@1.18.0/dist/bootstrap-table.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
